OL,6,F"This coin is really significant
OL,7,Fbecause it's the first of that
OL,8,Fearliest type, the earliest coins to
OL,9,Factually have been minted outside of
OL,10,FCarlisle."
OL,12,FLater in David I's reign coins were
OL,13,Fproduced in a variety of places
OL,14,Fincluding Perth, Berwick-upon-Tweed,
OL,15,FSt Andrews, and in the Scottish
OL,16,FBorders at Roxburgh.
